Subject: [PATCH v3 2/3] arm64: dts: ti: k3-am65: Add general purpose timers for am65
Date:   Tue, 15 Nov 2022 17:48:41 +0200
Message-Id: <20221115154842.7755-3-tony@atomide.com>
